                ul
                    li Check-in: After **14:00 GMT+1** on Sunday, 23rd February, or Monday, 24th February.
                    li Check-out: Before **12:00 GMT+1** on your departure day.

                .faq-item
                h4 Q: Is this program suitable for beginners in Generative AI?
                p Yes, the program is designed for participants at various levels, including beginners. It offers an opportunity to deepen your knowledge and engage with peers and experts in the field.

            // Cancellations and Modifications
