                .faq-item
                h4 Q: Can I modify my reservations after submitting the form?
                p Yes, you can update your reservation details by re-submitting the form and notifying us via email. Please notify us at least two weeks before the event for logistical purposes.

                .faq-item
                h4 Q: Will I get a refund if I cancel my reservation?
